\title{SENSITIVITY ANALYSIS AND STATISTICAL CONVERGENCE OF A SALTATING PARTICLE MODEL}

\author{Sergio Maldonado
\thanks{
PhD Candidate, Institute for Energy Systems, School of Engineering, The University of Edinburgh, The King's Buildings, Edinburgh EH9 3JL, U.K. E-mail: S.Mal-Vil@ed.ac.uk Tel: +44 (0)131 651 7293. Fax: +44 (0)131 650 6554} and Alistair G.L. Borthwick
